<doc f='llvm/llvm/include/llvm/Transforms/Utils/CallPromotionUtils.h' l='33'>/// Promote the given indirect call site to unconditionally call \p Callee.
///
/// This function promotes the given call site, returning the direct call or
/// invoke instruction. If the function type of the call site doesn&apos;t match that
/// of the callee, bitcast instructions are inserted where appropriate. If \p
/// RetBitCast is non-null, it will be used to store the return value bitcast,
/// if created.</doc>
